00:01:13.582 --> 00:01:14.749 line:90%
Your Majesty.

00:01:35.645 --> 00:01:40.567 line:90%
THE EAST PALACE

00:01:41.943 --> 00:01:46.448 line:90%
Yeom-mae? I cannot hear you. Speak louder.

00:01:48.325 --> 00:01:50.660 line:90%
Why is it so cramped in here?

00:01:50.744 --> 00:01:52.621 line:90%
What am I, some kind of grub?

00:01:52.704 --> 00:01:54.915 line:90%
Is this really the only place
you could hide me?

00:01:55.665 --> 00:01:56.958 line:90%
What is he saying?

00:01:58.460 --> 00:02:01.296 line:90%
Come closer and speak.

00:02:01.796 --> 00:02:03.089 line:90%
Through this hole.

00:02:15.644 --> 00:02:18.146 line:90%
Perhaps I should quit now. Heavens.

00:02:18.229 --> 00:02:19.814 line:90%
Would you stop complaining?

00:02:19.898 --> 00:02:22.859 line:90%
You were the one who chose to stay
when I told you to run.

00:02:22.943 --> 00:02:25.654 line:90%
I stayed because I vowed to save you
the way you saved me.

00:02:25.737 --> 00:02:27.280 line:90%
Are you scolding me now?

00:02:27.864 --> 00:02:31.242 line:90%
I begged my grandmother to hide you,
but you keep complaining.

00:02:31.326 --> 00:02:34.245 line:90%
So I am about to lose
all sense of guilt and gratitude.

00:02:34.746 --> 00:02:36.498 line:90%
Yeom-mae…

00:02:40.919 --> 00:02:42.587 line:90%
is difficult work by nature…

00:02:44.673 --> 00:02:46.466 line:90%
so I lost my temper for a moment.

00:02:46.549 --> 00:02:48.218 line:90%
So…

00:02:51.179 --> 00:02:53.890 line:90%
what exactly is this yeom-mae?

00:02:55.392 --> 00:02:56.309 line:90%
A cursing ritual.

00:02:57.644 --> 00:02:59.354 line:90%
A most vile one.

00:02:59.437 --> 00:03:02.816 line:90%
A ritual where someone is sealed in a jar
and starved to death…

00:03:04.818 --> 00:03:06.736 line:90%
so they become a won-gwi.

00:03:07.862 --> 00:03:10.949 line:90%
-But if--
-I cannot become a spirit in the water.

00:03:11.032 --> 00:03:12.575 line:90%
So this is the only way.

00:03:15.787 --> 00:03:17.080 line:90%
If you do that,

00:03:18.373 --> 00:03:20.333 line:90%
would the Crown Prince's spirit
be banished?

00:03:20.417 --> 00:03:21.876 line:90%
I have no power to do that.

00:03:21.960 --> 00:03:27.173 line:90%
All I can do is let my soul pass through
this small opening.

00:03:28.466 --> 00:03:33.096 line:90%
Instead, I will find a way to suppress
the power of the Crown Prince's spirit.

00:03:34.681 --> 00:03:35.849 line:90%
Then I will…

00:03:37.767 --> 00:03:42.105 line:90%
persuade Father not to have you killed.

00:03:42.731 --> 00:03:46.026 line:90%
But what if you snap at the King again
and get thrown out?

00:03:46.526 --> 00:03:48.528 line:90%
You both have a terrible temper.

00:03:49.779 --> 00:03:52.949 line:90%
Do not worry.
Just make sure you do not die.

00:03:54.200 --> 00:03:56.161 line:90%
You are the one who should not worry.

00:03:57.203 --> 00:04:00.957 line:90%
Do not follow me to the grave
for trying to help me.

00:04:11.301 --> 00:04:12.135 line:90%
Now, then.

00:04:12.635 --> 00:04:15.722 line:90%
Please seal this hole as well.

00:05:20.537 --> 00:05:21.913 line:90%
<i>Where is he?</i>

00:05:22.413 --> 00:05:24.457 line:90%
I cannot tell you.

00:05:25.625 --> 00:05:28.503 line:90%
Not until you promise not to kill him.

00:05:28.586 --> 00:05:30.755 line:90%
Now that Prince Yeongan is dead,

00:05:31.464 --> 00:05:33.633 line:90%
his role in the palace is over.

00:05:33.716 --> 00:05:36.845 line:90%
The spirit has not been banished yet,
so we still need him.

00:05:36.928 --> 00:05:38.429 line:90%
He has already failed.

00:05:39.013 --> 00:05:42.183 line:90%
I will not give that incompetent wretch
another chance.

00:05:42.267 --> 00:05:45.478 line:90%
It is because you never told him
who the spirit truly was.

00:05:51.067 --> 00:05:53.194 line:90%
You must now acknowledge the truth.

00:05:53.278 --> 00:05:57.073 line:90%
If you kill Gu-cheon to hide
that the Crown Prince is the spirit,

00:05:58.241 --> 00:06:00.201 line:90%
we will soon share Prince Yeongan's fate.

00:06:03.788 --> 00:06:06.332 line:90%
As of this moment,
you are dismissed from the palace.

00:06:06.833 --> 00:06:07.750 line:90%
Leave at once.

00:06:07.834 --> 00:06:09.627 line:90%
I cannot do that.

00:06:09.711 --> 00:06:11.254 line:90%
If you disappear,

00:06:11.337 --> 00:06:15.216 line:90%
there will be no one left to… help him.

00:06:15.842 --> 00:06:16.801 line:90%
Then…

00:06:19.637 --> 00:06:22.140 line:90%
I will reveal
your shameful secret, Father.

00:06:22.724 --> 00:06:24.601 line:90%
There was never any pond spirit.

00:06:24.684 --> 00:06:27.729 line:90%
Because you were the one
who killed the late king's son!

00:06:34.027 --> 00:06:39.115 line:90%
Unless you wish to die like your mother,
never speak those words again.

00:06:40.200 --> 00:06:41.159 line:90%
Where is he?

00:06:44.329 --> 00:06:46.080 line:90%
So was it you, Father?

00:06:47.916 --> 00:06:50.919 line:90%
-Did you kill my mother as well?
-I will ask you again.

00:06:51.502 --> 00:06:54.380 line:90%
-Where is Gu-cheon?
-I will ask you again.

00:06:56.799 --> 00:06:58.760 line:90%
Did you kill Mother?

00:07:07.393 --> 00:07:08.937 line:90%
Chief Eunuch!

00:07:09.938 --> 00:07:12.273 line:90%
Confine the Princess to her quarters.

00:07:12.357 --> 00:07:17.153 line:90%
Keep a close watch
so she cannot take a single step outside.

00:07:35.546 --> 00:07:38.716 line:90%
That ungrateful little bastard.

00:07:39.217 --> 00:07:41.177 line:90%
It is eating it all by itself.

00:08:49.537 --> 00:08:51.414 line:90%
<i>A deep resentment</i>

00:08:51.914 --> 00:08:54.042 line:90%
<i>has reached every corner.</i>

00:08:56.753 --> 00:08:58.880 line:90%
<i>At this rate, the Princess,</i>

00:09:00.423 --> 00:09:02.342 line:90%
<i>the life of the King</i>…

00:09:05.887 --> 00:09:07.055 line:90%
Royal Noble Consort…

00:09:08.264 --> 00:09:10.058 line:90%
Request Royal Noble Consort Sukbin…

00:09:25.823 --> 00:09:29.035 line:90%
Why are you asking
about the late Crown Prince?

00:09:29.535 --> 00:09:33.873 line:90%
Are there any
of the Crown Prince's belongings left?

00:09:36.417 --> 00:09:38.920 line:90%
I hid you at Saeng-gang's request,

00:09:39.003 --> 00:09:41.672 line:90%
and you summoned me here
to say such nonsense?

00:09:42.256 --> 00:09:45.635 line:90%
Your purpose should be to capture
the spirit tormenting His Majesty.

00:09:45.718 --> 00:09:47.178 line:90%
Why would…

00:09:49.972 --> 00:09:52.433 line:90%
the Crown Prince bear such resentment
toward His Majesty?

00:09:54.102 --> 00:09:55.103 line:90%
Are you saying

00:09:56.312 --> 00:09:58.231 line:90%
the one who is cursing the royal family

00:09:59.315 --> 00:10:00.817 line:90%
is the late Crown Prince?

00:10:00.900 --> 00:10:01.776 line:90%
How dare you!

00:10:01.859 --> 00:10:04.237 line:90%
So this is why His Majesty
is looking for you.

00:10:04.987 --> 00:10:06.781 line:90%
Will you lose your granddaughter as well?

00:10:07.824 --> 00:10:09.075 line:90%
At this rate…

00:10:10.993 --> 00:10:12.870 line:90%
your son and granddaughter

00:10:14.414 --> 00:10:17.458 line:90%
will cough up blood and die,
one after the other.

00:10:20.336 --> 00:10:25.341 line:90%
The villagers near Goyang-hyeon
are refusing labor duty, claiming illness?

00:10:27.510 --> 00:10:28.970 line:90%
What illness, exactly?

00:10:29.053 --> 00:10:31.431 line:90%
It appears to be merely a cold,
Your Majesty.

00:10:31.514 --> 00:10:35.268 line:90%
All the able-bodied men have fallen ill.

00:10:35.351 --> 00:10:38.104 line:90%
The village lies beneath a great mountain,

00:10:38.187 --> 00:10:40.064 line:90%
and its cold air brings on such illness.

00:10:40.565 --> 00:10:42.650 line:90%
Your Majesty, what matters is…

00:10:43.526 --> 00:10:46.487 line:90%
Your Majesty,
the seat of the Crown Prince is vacant.

00:10:46.571 --> 00:10:49.782 line:90%
You must appoint
one of the royal kin to the seat.

00:10:49.866 --> 00:10:52.493 line:90%
-There is no time to lose--
-Who do you mean?

00:10:53.995 --> 00:10:56.664 line:90%
You mean the son of Prince Iksang?

00:10:57.373 --> 00:10:59.917 line:90%
Did you not all see him collapse
with your own eyes

00:11:00.001 --> 00:11:04.046 line:90%
at the banquet on the 70th birthday
of the Queen Dowager?

00:11:04.130 --> 00:11:07.049 line:90%
Do you wish me to appoint
such a flawed child as Crown Prince?

00:11:07.133 --> 00:11:09.760 line:90%
It is still too soon
to appoint a Crown Prince.

00:11:10.344 --> 00:11:12.805 line:90%
I am still in good health,

00:11:12.889 --> 00:11:16.142 line:90%
so do not speak such words…

00:11:28.738 --> 00:11:30.281 line:90%
Your Majesty!

00:12:36.222 --> 00:12:39.350 line:90%
You dare go around stirring up trouble
in the palace.

00:12:44.814 --> 00:12:46.023 line:90%
Do you see this?

00:12:51.862 --> 00:12:55.074 line:90%
This Ikseongwan crown was made
for Prince Yeongan.

00:12:57.285 --> 00:12:58.744 line:90%
But that child

00:13:00.246 --> 00:13:01.872 line:90%
is now gone.

00:13:03.416 --> 00:13:04.959 line:90%
All because of you.

00:13:08.170 --> 00:13:11.507 line:90%
I will risk everything to track you down.

00:13:11.591 --> 00:13:12.842 line:90%
I will find you…

00:13:15.094 --> 00:13:16.929 line:90%
and I will…

00:13:21.392 --> 00:13:22.852 line:90%
at all costs…

00:13:36.824 --> 00:13:38.451 line:90%
Damn it.

00:13:40.036 --> 00:13:41.621 line:90%
I should have fled.

00:13:42.705 --> 00:13:45.666 line:90%
The King is combing through the palace?

00:13:46.167 --> 00:13:49.670 line:90%
Has he lost his mind
now that his last son is dead?

00:13:49.754 --> 00:13:52.798 line:90%
It seems he is searching
for a man called Gu-cheon.

00:13:54.050 --> 00:13:57.595 line:90%
He failed in his task,
so he should have tried to flee.

00:14:01.265 --> 00:14:02.141 line:90%
As you wish.

00:14:08.522 --> 00:14:10.024 line:90%
How are things in the palace?

00:14:12.568 --> 00:14:15.404 line:90%
The power of the spirit has spread
throughout the palace.

00:14:16.030 --> 00:14:18.032 line:90%
Even I nearly fainted.

00:14:19.617 --> 00:14:23.788 line:90%
The King's life
is now hanging by a thread.

00:14:24.288 --> 00:14:26.832 line:90%
But what troubles me is Gu-cheon.

00:14:28.209 --> 00:14:31.045 line:90%
I fear he may become a lifeline
for the King.

00:14:33.047 --> 00:14:35.591 line:90%
Then we should

00:14:36.550 --> 00:14:39.220 line:90%
cut that lifeline, should we not?

00:14:50.064 --> 00:14:54.318 line:90%
Your Highness,
His Majesty urgently summons you.

00:14:55.736 --> 00:14:58.948 line:90%
I thought I was not to take a single step
outside my quarters.

00:14:59.573 --> 00:15:01.867 line:90%
His Majesty intends to leave the palace
for a short while.

00:15:03.160 --> 00:15:05.496 line:90%
He wishes you to accompany him.

00:15:36.736 --> 00:15:37.820 line:90%
Halt.

00:15:40.865 --> 00:15:42.825 line:90%
-Check the surroundings.
-Yes, sir.

00:15:47.872 --> 00:15:48.956 line:90%
Very well.

00:15:53.878 --> 00:15:54.962 line:90%
Your Majesty.

00:15:56.464 --> 00:16:00.468 line:90%
They look like refugees with the elderly
and children among them.

00:16:01.010 --> 00:16:02.762 line:90%
It appears they stay here

00:16:02.845 --> 00:16:04.889 line:90%
because their illness worsened
while fleeing.

00:16:05.848 --> 00:16:09.018 line:90%
-It is close to Goyang-hyeon--
-I will see them myself.

00:16:09.101 --> 00:16:10.186 line:90%
Yes, Your Majesty.

00:16:37.505 --> 00:16:38.923 line:90%
Goyang-hyeon…

00:16:41.258 --> 00:16:43.219 line:90%
I should look around the nearby villages.

00:16:44.094 --> 00:16:47.223 line:90%
-Then the memorial rite…
-We will stop by before performing it.

00:16:48.182 --> 00:16:51.352 line:90%
Were you intending to go to the tomb
of the late Crown Prince?

00:16:53.646 --> 00:16:55.564 line:90%
We will perform a rite there.

00:16:55.648 --> 00:16:58.359 line:90%
So did you mean to kill Gu-cheon,
trusting in the rite?

00:16:59.235 --> 00:17:02.905 line:90%
It will not work.
You will need Gu-cheon in the end.

00:17:02.988 --> 00:17:06.784 line:90%
-You must spare his life.
-You two stay here and tend to the people.

00:17:07.284 --> 00:17:08.118 line:90%
To the village.

00:17:20.005 --> 00:17:22.883 line:90%
Come on, you need to eat something.

00:17:22.967 --> 00:17:23.968 line:90%
Sir.

00:17:24.468 --> 00:17:25.678 line:90%
Sir!

00:17:25.761 --> 00:17:26.846 line:90%
No.

00:17:27.388 --> 00:17:28.472 line:90%
Sir.

00:17:29.723 --> 00:17:31.767 line:90%
Please save my Gi-dong's mother.

00:17:31.851 --> 00:17:35.563 line:90%
The blisters have spread up to her throat,
and her whole body is burning like fire.

00:17:35.646 --> 00:17:37.690 line:90%
What am I to do?

00:17:38.190 --> 00:17:41.193 line:90%
Please save her!

00:17:41.277 --> 00:17:42.862 line:90%
There is nothing I can do.

00:17:44.738 --> 00:17:46.448 line:90%
Stay with me!

00:17:46.532 --> 00:17:48.409 line:90%
My dear!

00:17:55.374 --> 00:17:56.709 line:90%
A strange pestilence.

00:17:56.792 --> 00:17:58.335 line:90%
Is there no way

00:17:58.961 --> 00:18:00.421 line:90%
to cure it?

00:18:01.005 --> 00:18:02.006 line:90%
There is none.

00:18:02.715 --> 00:18:04.633 line:90%
I do not even know what illness it is.

00:18:05.593 --> 00:18:10.431 line:90%
When one falls ill, the entire family
is stricken by the next day.

00:18:14.518 --> 00:18:18.022 line:90%
Now every household
is boiling peach branches to drink.

00:18:18.564 --> 00:18:20.649 line:90%
They say a spirit brought the illness.

00:18:25.279 --> 00:18:28.240 line:90%
My lord!

00:18:29.867 --> 00:18:34.121 line:90%
My lord, please help save my father.

00:18:34.788 --> 00:18:36.415 line:90%
Just like my older brother,

00:18:38.042 --> 00:18:39.627 line:90%
he is not breathing.

00:18:39.710 --> 00:18:40.711 line:90%
What insolence.

00:18:44.006 --> 00:18:45.382 line:90%
Forgive me.

00:19:04.610 --> 00:19:06.278 line:90%
I am so scared.

00:19:09.865 --> 00:19:10.908 line:90%
I understand.

00:19:10.991 --> 00:19:14.203 line:90%
Go and tend to this child and her family.

00:19:14.286 --> 00:19:15.204 line:90%
Yes, Your Majesty.

00:19:16.705 --> 00:19:17.706 line:90%
Come here.

00:19:23.963 --> 00:19:25.422 line:90%
It is an unknown pestilence.

00:19:26.882 --> 00:19:28.092 line:90%
A highly contagious one.

00:19:36.642 --> 00:19:38.352 line:90%
We will return to the palace at once.

00:19:39.103 --> 00:19:40.646 line:90%
What shall we do about the rite?

00:19:40.729 --> 00:19:41.897 line:90%
It will be postponed.

00:19:42.398 --> 00:19:44.858 line:90%
-We must stop the pestilence.
-Your Majesty.

00:19:46.110 --> 00:19:49.238 line:90%
What shall we do
about the villagers dying here?

00:19:49.321 --> 00:19:52.533 line:90%
At this rate,
all the people will be in danger.

00:19:53.283 --> 00:19:54.368 line:90%
Hurry.

00:20:12.428 --> 00:20:14.680 line:90%
This is a poem
written by the Crown Prince.

00:20:15.472 --> 00:20:20.644 line:90%
Ever since he was a child,
he would send me his poems in his letters.

00:20:22.021 --> 00:20:25.691 line:90%
That is the only thing
the Crown Prince left behind.

00:20:29.820 --> 00:20:30.988 line:90%
From now on,

00:20:32.531 --> 00:20:35.159 line:90%
you must do as I say.

00:20:40.789 --> 00:20:44.251 line:90%
<i>Go to the study of the Crown Prince,</i>
<i>remove the latch,</i>

00:20:45.627 --> 00:20:47.629 line:90%
<i>and post the Crown Prince's poem</i>
<i>on the door.</i>

00:20:50.716 --> 00:20:53.469 line:90%
<i>Before his power grows stronger,</i>

00:20:54.178 --> 00:20:55.721 line:90%
<i>he must be sealed.</i>

00:21:06.565 --> 00:21:10.527 line:90%
<i>Find Gu-cheon hiding in the palace.</i>

00:21:11.904 --> 00:21:14.865 line:90%
<i>I will trace his steps</i>
<i>from where he had been.</i>

00:21:17.284 --> 00:21:19.328 line:90%
<i>Even the smallest trace</i>

00:21:19.828 --> 00:21:21.080 line:90%
<i>will lead me to him.</i>

00:21:46.313 --> 00:21:47.314 line:90%
There he is.

00:22:15.801 --> 00:22:18.303 line:90%
-They say they found him in the shrine.
-Very well.

00:22:18.804 --> 00:22:19.721 line:90%
Your Majesty.

00:22:22.099 --> 00:22:23.600 line:90%
They have found Gu-cheon.

00:22:28.188 --> 00:22:29.273 line:90%
Kill him.

00:22:30.649 --> 00:22:31.608 line:90%
No.

00:22:31.692 --> 00:22:33.777 line:90%
Father, you must not.

00:22:34.278 --> 00:22:35.696 line:90%
We need him.

00:22:35.779 --> 00:22:37.489 line:90%
Father, you must not!

00:22:37.573 --> 00:22:38.866 line:90%
You have to spare him!

00:22:39.533 --> 00:22:40.784 line:90%
Father!

00:22:42.828 --> 00:22:43.704 line:90%
Drag him out!

00:22:44.413 --> 00:22:45.330 line:90%
No.

00:22:52.713 --> 00:22:53.839 line:90%
Let go.

00:23:12.608 --> 00:23:14.985 line:90%
No.

00:23:27.206 --> 00:23:28.749 line:90%
Get up.

00:23:30.792 --> 00:23:31.919 line:90%
Let go of me.

00:23:33.086 --> 00:23:34.129 line:90%
I said let go!

00:23:36.548 --> 00:23:37.591 line:90%
Easy now.

00:23:38.800 --> 00:23:40.052 line:90%
You are far too hasty.

00:23:46.225 --> 00:23:47.768 line:90%
The Buddha is watching.

00:23:48.602 --> 00:23:51.188 line:90%
-Take him somewhere out of sight.
-Yes, sir.

00:23:59.446 --> 00:24:02.616 line:90%
-Everyone will die.
-Lost your senses with death so near?

00:24:11.041 --> 00:24:12.960 line:90%
What are you muttering?

00:24:16.129 --> 00:24:18.590 line:90%
That the King will die.

00:24:43.031 --> 00:24:45.492 line:90%
-Where is His Majesty?
-He is inside.

00:24:45.575 --> 00:24:46.827 line:90%
Is something wrong?

00:24:47.995 --> 00:24:48.996 line:90%
Your Majesty.

00:24:54.668 --> 00:24:55.627 line:90%
Your Majesty.

00:24:56.586 --> 00:24:57.462 line:90%
Your Majesty!

00:24:58.088 --> 00:24:59.756 line:90%
-Your Majesty!
-Your Majesty!

00:25:02.134 --> 00:25:03.677 line:90%
Your Majesty!

00:25:05.929 --> 00:25:07.556 line:90%
-Your Majesty!
-Your Majesty!

00:25:07.639 --> 00:25:10.142 line:90%
Bring the royal physician! The physician!

00:25:10.225 --> 00:25:12.019 line:90%
-Yes, sir.
-Your Majesty!

00:25:12.102 --> 00:25:14.354 line:90%
Your Majesty!

00:25:15.981 --> 00:25:19.651 line:90%
The King is going to die?

00:25:20.235 --> 00:25:25.157 line:90%
Word has spread throughout the palace
that His Majesty may not last the night.

00:25:28.452 --> 00:25:33.582 line:90%
Just as that vile spirit cursed,

00:25:35.292 --> 00:25:40.172 line:90%
will the royal bloodline be cut off?

00:25:41.548 --> 00:25:42.424 line:90%
Pardon?

00:25:43.675 --> 00:25:46.470 line:90%
Your Majesty, what do you…

00:25:49.806 --> 00:25:53.393 line:90%
Dispatch a man to Prince Iksang.

00:26:00.108 --> 00:26:01.401 line:90%
This is your retribution.

00:26:03.070 --> 00:26:06.656 line:90%
Consider this the price
for the evil deeds…

00:26:08.992 --> 00:26:11.453 line:90%
you committed 30 years ago, Father.

00:26:52.661 --> 00:26:54.287 line:90%
Where is he?

00:27:09.594 --> 00:27:11.054 line:90%
Why are you all standing around?

00:27:12.305 --> 00:27:13.723 line:90%
Untie him at once!

00:27:13.807 --> 00:27:15.058 line:90%
Untie him.

00:27:32.826 --> 00:27:34.870 line:90%
You certainly took your time.

00:27:34.953 --> 00:27:36.163 line:90%
Indeed.

00:27:37.122 --> 00:27:38.665 line:90%
You look awful.

00:27:39.458 --> 00:27:41.126 line:90%
If the King has collapsed,

00:27:42.711 --> 00:27:45.297 line:90%
you cannot be safe either.

00:27:47.048 --> 00:27:48.383 line:90%
Are you all right?

00:27:51.219 --> 00:27:52.846 line:90%
I am fine.

00:27:55.724 --> 00:27:57.017 line:90%
But more importantly,

00:27:58.477 --> 00:28:00.645 line:90%
Father is in critical condition.

00:28:01.396 --> 00:28:04.649 line:90%
Is there any way
to banish the spirit right now?

00:28:07.068 --> 00:28:08.361 line:90%
The body.

00:28:09.696 --> 00:28:12.240 line:90%
The body of the Crown Prince.

00:28:38.850 --> 00:28:43.230 line:90%
Bring the body of the Crown Prince
to the palace at once.

00:28:43.313 --> 00:28:45.232 line:90%
What are you saying, Your Highness?

00:28:45.315 --> 00:28:46.358 line:90%
There is no time.

00:28:46.441 --> 00:28:48.360 line:90%
This is to save Father.

00:28:49.361 --> 00:28:51.863 line:90%
We cannot desecrate a royal tomb.

00:28:52.489 --> 00:28:56.660 line:90%
-That would be high treason--
-I will bear full responsibility.

00:28:58.161 --> 00:28:59.538 line:90%
And once Father awakens,

00:28:59.621 --> 00:29:04.334 line:90%
I will bear the punishment
for insulting the royal house as well.

00:29:09.047 --> 00:29:12.676 line:90%
<i>To banish the spirit,</i>
<i>we need the body of the Crown Prince.</i>

00:29:15.971 --> 00:29:19.599 line:90%
<i>But we must not let the spirit find out.</i>

00:29:20.100 --> 00:29:23.520 line:90%
<i>So we must deceive it using a dead animal.</i>

00:29:26.022 --> 00:29:29.568 line:90%
<i>If we fail to drive it away before dawn,</i>

00:29:31.403 --> 00:29:33.613 line:90%
<i>the King is fated to die.</i>

00:29:35.156 --> 00:29:39.869 line:90%
<i>All that remains is for me</i>
<i>to strike the spirit down with my blade.</i>

00:29:47.294 --> 00:29:49.212 line:90%
Can you truly do it?

00:29:50.005 --> 00:29:51.214 line:90%
In that condition?

00:29:51.715 --> 00:29:54.759 line:90%
I may be half-dead,
but what choice do I have?

00:29:59.848 --> 00:30:03.643 line:90%
Thanks to the King's collapse,
I get some fresh air.

00:30:03.727 --> 00:30:05.979 line:90%
Are you joking at a time like this?

00:30:06.813 --> 00:30:10.150 line:90%
That is why you must not forget
what I told you to do.

00:30:13.653 --> 00:30:15.113 line:90%
Do not worry.

00:30:16.489 --> 00:30:18.533 line:90%
And stop frowning.

00:30:21.369 --> 00:30:22.370 line:90%
Gu-cheon.

00:30:32.422 --> 00:30:34.049 line:90%
You told me before.

00:30:35.133 --> 00:30:38.720 line:90%
That your own life matters
more than that of anyone else.

00:30:39.971 --> 00:30:42.265 line:90%
That you do not want to die
and become an ak-gwi.

00:30:42.974 --> 00:30:44.726 line:90%
That is still true.

00:30:50.523 --> 00:30:51.816 line:90%
Then that is enough.

00:31:03.495 --> 00:31:04.704 line:90%
Do not foolishly…

00:31:07.248 --> 00:31:09.376 line:90%
die for me.

00:31:13.088 --> 00:31:14.506 line:90%
Needless to say.

00:32:25.827 --> 00:32:29.789 line:90%
<i>You must bind the body of the Crown Prince</i>
<i>tightly with this bloodstained rope.</i>

00:32:31.750 --> 00:32:33.877 line:90%
There is one more thing
you must bear in mind.

00:32:33.960 --> 00:32:36.045 line:90%
Bind the door shut with the rope.

00:32:37.589 --> 00:32:39.174 line:90%
<i>And no matter what happens,</i>

00:32:39.674 --> 00:32:41.551 line:90%
<i>do not open it.</i>

00:32:44.220 --> 00:32:45.889 line:90%
<i>If I fail,</i>

00:32:47.390 --> 00:32:49.309 line:90%
<i>you will be the next target.</i>

00:33:01.112 --> 00:33:02.906 line:90%
Insolent wretch.

00:33:02.989 --> 00:33:04.449 line:90%
You are doing this in vain.

00:33:13.708 --> 00:33:15.960 line:90%
Do not meddle in this matter.

00:33:17.086 --> 00:33:19.589 line:90%
I must sever the royal bloodline.

00:33:20.882 --> 00:33:22.634 line:90%
I cannot allow that.

00:33:23.259 --> 00:33:26.012 line:90%
There is someone in this palace
I wish to save.

00:33:58.127 --> 00:34:00.129 line:90%
It is all over now.

00:34:10.181 --> 00:34:11.224 line:90%
What is that?

00:34:14.811 --> 00:34:17.272 line:90%
It does not appear to be a gwi-mae.

00:34:18.940 --> 00:34:21.317 line:90%
Good heavens. I cannot believe this.

00:34:22.485 --> 00:34:24.320 line:90%
Whose presiding deity is this?

00:34:24.821 --> 00:34:27.156 line:90%
Who on earth is interfering?

00:34:36.249 --> 00:34:37.625 line:90%
<i>Very well.</i>

00:34:37.709 --> 00:34:42.130 line:90%
<i>How powerful will the presiding deity</i>
<i>you serve be?</i>

00:34:43.339 --> 00:34:45.049 line:90%
<i>Let us see.</i>

00:34:56.519 --> 00:34:57.812 line:90%
The Crown Prince's spirit.

00:36:09.842 --> 00:36:13.429 line:90%
Not knowing your true identity,
I cannot even send you to the heavens.

00:36:23.773 --> 00:36:28.277 line:90%
Here we go! The grim elder!

00:37:22.457 --> 00:37:24.792 line:90%
You shaman wretch…

00:37:34.761 --> 00:37:36.387 line:90%
Something is wrong.

00:37:40.391 --> 00:37:42.852 line:90%
Your Highness!

00:37:42.935 --> 00:37:43.853 line:90%
What is it?

00:37:43.936 --> 00:37:45.772 line:90%
Please open the door.

00:37:45.855 --> 00:37:47.857 line:90%
Something terrible has happened
to Gu-cheon.

00:37:47.940 --> 00:37:50.318 line:90%
You need to get to the pond now!

00:37:50.902 --> 00:37:52.236 line:90%
Please hurry.

00:37:53.404 --> 00:37:55.031 line:90%
-Hurry.
-Very well.

00:37:55.782 --> 00:37:58.076 line:90%
Your Highness! Hurry!

00:37:59.160 --> 00:38:00.369 line:90%
Please hurry.

00:38:15.760 --> 00:38:17.220 line:90%
You know nothing.

00:38:20.014 --> 00:38:21.224 line:90%
Nothing at all.

00:39:31.169 --> 00:39:32.378 line:90%
A gwi-mae…

00:39:58.696 --> 00:39:59.572 line:90%
Enough.

00:40:01.490 --> 00:40:02.867 line:90%
That is enough!

00:43:42.044 --> 00:43:45.297 line:90%
Subtitle translation by: Yun-hee Jang